@startuml AdminSec_UC02-30_Templates_Documents
title UC-02-30: Gerer Templates et Documents - AdminSecretariat (Tous Scenarios)

actor AdminSecretariat as A
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Storage
participant Logs

A -> Dashboard: 1. Accede a Templates et Documents
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> DB: 2. Recupere templates (verifier secretariat_id)
activate DB

alt Erreur BD
  DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: BD indisponible
  deactivate DB
  Dashboard --> A: ERREUR 500: Impossible charger templates
  deactivate Dashboard
else BD disponible
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne templates (contrats, lettres, releves)
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> A: 3. Affiche catalogue templates
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 4. Clique Creer Template
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard --> A: 5. Affiche editeur template avec variables ({nom}, {salaire}, etc)
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 6. Redige template et clique Sauvegarder
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> Systeme: 7. Valide syntaxe variables et structure template
  activate Systeme

  alt Template invalide (variables mal formees)
    Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Syntaxe variables invalide
    deactivate Systeme
    Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Template contient variables invalides
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Template valide
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard -> DB: 8. Cree et enregistre template
    activate DB

    alt Erreur BD
      DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Creation echouee
      deactivate DB
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Impossible sauvegarder template
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Creation OK
      DB -> DB: 9. INSERT template (nom, contenu, secretariat_id, timestamp)

      DB --> Dashboard: Template cree
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> DB: 10. Enregistre log audit: Cree template (admin, nom, timestamp, secretariat_id)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 11. Log event: Template cree
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> A: 12. SUCCES! Template cree
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over A, Logs
        **TEMPLATE CREE OK:**
        - Template sauvegarde
        - Variables validees
        - DB: Audit logs persistes
        - Logs: Events loggues
      end note
    end
  end

  A -> Dashboard: 13. Clique sur template existant
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> DB: 14. Recupere template (verifier secretariat_id)
  activate DB

  alt Template inexistant ou n'appartient pas au secretariat
    DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR 404 ou 403: Non trouve ou acces refuse
    deactivate DB
    Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Template inexistant ou acces refuse
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Template existe
    DB --> Dashboard: Retourne template (contenu, metadata)
    deactivate DB

    Dashboard --> A: 15. Affiche template avec options
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 16. Clique Generer Document
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard --> A: 17. Affiche form parametres (selectionnez client/employe)
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 18. Selectionne employe et clique Generer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 19. Recupere donnees employe et client
    activate Systeme

    Systeme -> DB: 20. Charge infos employe (verifier secretariat_id)
    activate DB

    alt Employe inexistant ou n'appartient pas au secretariat
      DB --> Systeme: ERREUR 404 ou 403: Non trouve ou acces refuse
      deactivate DB
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Employe inexistant ou acces refuse
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Employe inexistant ou acces refuse
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Employe existe
      DB --> Systeme: Retourne donnees employe (nom, salaire, poste)
      deactivate DB

      Systeme -> Systeme: 21. Remplace variables du template avec donnees

      Systeme --> Dashboard: Document genere
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> Storage: 22. Sauvegarde document genere en PDF (MinIO)
      activate Storage

      alt Storage indisponible
        Storage --> Dashboard: ERREUR 503: MinIO indisponible
        deactivate Storage
        Dashboard -> Logs: Log tentative generation doc: MinIO DOWN
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue
        deactivate Logs
        Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Service stockage indisponible
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Storage OK
        Storage --> Dashboard: Document stocke + URL genere
        deactivate Storage

        Dashboard -> DB: 23. Enregistre trace generation (audit)
        activate DB

        DB -> DB: 24. INSERT generation_log (template_id, employe_id, timestamp, secretariat_id)

        DB --> Dashboard: Generation tracee
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> DB: 25. Enregistre log audit: Generation document (admin, template, employe, timestamp, secretariat_id)
        activate DB
        DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Logs: 26. Log event: Document genere
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
        deactivate Logs

        Dashboard --> A: 27. SUCCES! Document genere\nTelechargeable
        deactivate Dashboard

        note over A, Logs
          **DOCUMENT GENERE OK:**
          - Variables remplacees
          - PDF stocke (MinIO)
          - DB: Audit logs persistes
          - Logs: Events loggues
          - Acces IsOle au secretariat
        end note
      end
    end
  end
end

@enduml
